Steps to Install VS Code on ARM64
 
1. Update system package lists
     
     sudo apt update && sudo apt upgrade -y

2. Download VS Code for ARM64
     
     wget -O vscode_arm64.deb "https://code.visualstudio.com/sha/download?build=stable&os=linux-deb-arm64"

3.  Check if the file is downloaded

     ls -l vscode_arm64.deb

4. Install the .deb package

     sudo dpkg -i vscode_arm64.deb

5.  Fix missing dependencies (if installation fails)

     sudo apt --fix-broken install -y
     sudo dpkg -i vscode_arm64.deb

6. Launch VS Code

     code

7. Check if VS Code is installed correctly

     code --version


